name: SEAT
description:
Following the OBJKT4OBJKT event, I put this work here.

SEAT is a visualization of each illustrators has different ways in building their mood in order to go back to their "seat" for dealing with deadlines, sometimes they find their mood by go shopping, sleeping, or by cooking.

Yet for me, I'm bringing my mood back through self project, by doing something or painting something that am not used to.

Acrylic on cold press paper
2500px X 3600px

Personal use only. For commercial use please contact me through social media.
